{"arkId":"cl010112654","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010112654","modified ":"2026-01-14","title":"Astrolabe planisph\u00e9rique","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Astrolabe planisph\u00e9rique"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Ottomans (Islam-\u003E\u00e9poque islamique-\u003E\u00e9poque islamique 3 (1516-1798))\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1586 - 1587 (an 995 de l\u0027h\u00e9gire) (dat\u00e9 sur l\u0027oeuvre)","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 609 - Nicolas et Simone Landau, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 609, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1586,"endYear":1587,"imprecision":"","text":"4e quart du XVIe si\u00e8cle = dernier quart du XVIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"L-SH\u012aR\u0100Z\u012a, Khal\u012bfa","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Fabricant, facteur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 11951","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"instrument scientifique (mesure, calcul, observation, etc.)","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"L\u0027astrolabe est gradu\u00e9 sur son limbe d\u0027une \u00e9chelle de 360 degr\u00e9s. Au dos figurent une \u00e9chelle semi-circulaire de deux fois 90 degr\u00e9s, une \u00e9chelle des ombres, un carr\u00e9 des ombres, et dans le quadrant sup\u00e9rieur gauche un graphique des cosinus. L\u0027araign\u00e9e, dont seule la partie \u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur de l\u0027\u00e9cliptique a subsist\u00e9, porte le nom de trois \u00e9toiles seulement. Cinq tympans pour les latitudes de 21\u00b0 \u00e0 44\u00b0 sont compl\u00e9t\u00e9s par un sixi\u00e8me pour les horizons.","inscriptions":"Etiquette : \r ; \u0022707\u0022 (sur une \u00e9tiquette d\u00e9coll\u00e9e)\r ; Traduction : \r ; \u0022Cet astrolabe a \u00e9t\u00e9 fabriqu\u00e9 dans la ville d\u0027Alep la Grise, pour le service de l\u0027\u00e9mir Muhammad - que Dieu le prot\u00e8ge - par l\u0027humble Khalifa l-Shirazi al-Asturlabi en l\u0027ann\u00e9e 995\u0022 (signature et date sur la m\u00e8re)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Longueur","value":"28,2","displayDimension":"28,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"19,8","displayDimension":"19,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"0,8","displayDimension":"0,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"3","displayDimension":"3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Alliage cuivreux, \u00e9tain (pour la soudure)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : alliage cuivreux\r\nMat\u00e9riau : \u00e9tain (soudure)","placeOfCreation":"Alep (Asie occidentale = Proche-Orient = Proche orient-\u003ESyrie)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Ancielle collection Nicolas Landau, Paris ; don Mme Nicolas Landau, 2002","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Landau, Marcelle","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. Landau, Nicolas","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"28\/09\/2000","startYear":2000,"endYear":2000},{"type":"date du conseil artistique des mus\u00e9es nationaux","value":"04\/10\/2000","startYear":2000,"endYear":2000},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat